==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hyperventilation
<hw>hyperventilation</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or
process of hyperventilating; breathing rapidly and deeply.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A condition in which alveolar
carbon dioxide concentration is markedly lower than normal, usually due
to breathing rapidly and deeply.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>hypha</ent>⟦br⟧
